        "5. Write short HTML code to show your favorite fruits in a bulleted list and\n",
        "your top 3 programming languages in a numbered list."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "iZ7fBOGdao4H"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "Answer:-\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "```\n",
        "    <div>\n",
        "        <h4>My Favorite Fruits</h4>\n",
        "        <ul>\n",
        "            <li>Apple</li>\n",
        "            <li>Banana</li>\n",
        "            <li>Orange</li>\n",
        "            <li>Grapes</li>\n",
        "            <li>Mango</li>\n",
        "        </ul>\n",
        "        <h4>My Top 3 Programming Languages</h4>\n",
        "        <ol>\n",
        "            <li>JavaScript</li>\n",
        "            <li>React</li>\n",
        "            <li>Next.js</li>\n",
        "        </ol>\n",
        "   </div>\n",
        "```\n",
        "\n"
      ],
